        </div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-[#1c1917]">Passbook printing</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#6e6358]">No more handwriting entries. Each transaction prints clearly — type, amount, running balance — the moment it's recorded.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-[#e7e5e4] p-6 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-[#f0f7ef] flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-[#5b8c5a]">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 6v12M6 12h12"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-[#1c1917]">Cash position tracking</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#6e6358]">Every deposit and withdrawal updates counts in real time. Teller knows their position without counting. Manager sees totals across all tellers and the vault.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-[#e7e5e4] p-6 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-[#f0f7ef] flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-[#5b8c5a]">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v12a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h10a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V7a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-2"/><path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-[#1c1917]">End-of-day reconciliation</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#6e6358]">One click instead of 30 minutes of counting. The system compares expected vs actual cash and flags discrepancies immediately.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-[#e7e5e4] p-6 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-[#f0f7ef] flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-[#5b8c5a]">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M8 7h12M8 12h12M8 17h12M4 7h.01M4 12h.01M4 17h.01"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-[#1c1917]">Vault transfers</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#6e6358]">Moving cash between tellers or to vault is recorded instantly. No paper slips. Audit trail shows every movement and who approved it.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

